data.description: Welcome home! This conveniently located and well maintained 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom end unit townhouse is a rare find! This unit offers something most in the neighborhood do not. A FENCED in yard, which is the perfect outdoor space for relaxation or gatherings! Located in a well-established community, it offers generous living spaces with a floor plan that maximizes functionality and natural light. Meticulously maintained, this homes is a testament of true pride of ownership.
